		<title>Want Your Photos Critiqued? Join Us Live Today at 4pm on The Grid</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/AdobeLightroomKillerTips/~3/V-O8FYl9K60/</link>
		<comments>http://lightroomkillertips.com/2012/want-your-photos-critiqued-join-us-live-today-at-4pm-on-the-grid/#comments</comments>
