		<description><![CDATA[Hey everyone. For the last few months, Scott and I have been doing live photo critiques each month on our weekly talk show (The Grid). They&#8217;ve become [...]]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://lightroomkillertips.com/files/2012/06/thegrid_showcover.jpg"><img src="http://lightroomkillertips.com/files/2012/06/thegrid_showcover.jpg" alt="" width="590" height="350" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-4319" /></a><br />
Hey everyone. For the last few months, Scott and I have been doing live photo critiques each month on our weekly talk show (The Grid). They&#8217;ve become wildy popular and incredibly effective for not just the people who get their photos critiqued but also everyone else who gets to see the critique. It&#8217;s really eye opening to listen to what works/doesn&#8217;t work in a photo even if it&#8217;s not your own photos. So if you ever wanted go get in on the critiques you have another chance today. Our show goes live at 4pm EST. today. <a href="http://kelbytv.com/thegrid/critique/" target="_blank">You can submit your photos to get critiqued over on our page here</a> (no promises we can get to them but we&#8217;ll try our best). Hope you can at least stop by and check out the show. Thanks!</p>
